name: UNKNOWN_SEX
definition: Not known, observed, recorded; or reported as unknown by the data contributor.

name: FEMALE
definition: An animal who is observed by researcher or clinician to be female, the sex that ordinarily produces ova.

name: MALE
definition: An animal who is observed by researcher or clinician to be male, the sex that ordinarily produces sperm.

name: OTHER
definition: A person (one of unisexual specimens) who is born with genitalia and/or secondary sexual characteristics of indeterminate sex, or which combine features of both sexes.
